  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Company
    The company class is responsible for all the changes that happens within the employee list.
    Controller
    The controller class is responsible for the changes that happen in the graphical user interface.
    Date
    The date class helps with verifying if a given date is accurate (i.e.
    Employee
    The employee class is the superclass of every class that describes a different kind of employee.
    Fulltime
    The fulltime class is a subclass of the employee superclass.
    Main
    The Main class is responsible for executing the program and to display the graphical user interface.
    Management
    The management class is a subclass of our fulltime class.
    Parttime
    The parttime class is one of the subclasses of the Employee superclass.
    Profile
    The profile class defines and designs the personal information of an employee such as getting and setting up their name, department at which they work in, and when the company hired them.
